flowchart TD
    subgraph MH05["MH-05: Payment Flow Stripe Checkout"]
        P1[User clicks Book and Pay] --> P2[Backend creates Stripe Checkout Session]
        P2 --> P3[Redirect to Stripe hosted page]
        P3 --> P4{Payment result?}
        P4 -->|Success| P5[Stripe webhook: checkout.session.completed]
        P4 -->|Failed| P6[User returns to practice page]
        P4 -->|Abandoned| P7[Session expires after 30min]
        P5 --> P8[Payment Service creates booking]
        P8 --> P9[Notification Service confirms booking]
        P9 --> P10[Calendar Service schedules reminders]
        P6 --> P11[Show error + retry option]
        P7 --> P12[Log abandoned cart]
    end
